This algo uses Divide and conquer approach.
Maximum sub array sum is the maximum of the following results:

a. maximum sub array sum of left half (Recursive Function)
b. maximum sub array sum of right half (Recursive Function)
c. maximum sub array sum passing through mid element.(O(n))

[Source]: https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/maximum-subarray-sum-using-divide-and-conquer-algorithm/

*Additional Information*
Library: limits.h
used for macro such as INT_MIN.
